roperties of\n2DEG, is easily controlled by temperature. Such a splitting may also be induced\ninto states of functional surface layers deposited onto the surface of\nEuRh$_2$Si$_2$ or similarly ordered magnetic materials with metallic or\nsemiconducting properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Dec 2013 16:40:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-20"}
