rd refinements by Heyting and Kreisel) and the proof\ninterpretation by Orlov and Heyting (as clarified by G\\\"odel). While these two\ninterpretations are often conflated, from the viewpoint of the axioms of QHC\nneither of them reduces to the other one, although they do overlap.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Dec 2013 20:51:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Apr 2015 22:36:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 4 May 2015 00:38:00 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 1 May 2017 17:05:31 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sun, 2 Oct 2022 06:22:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-04"}
