hich the shell falls in near\ncounter-rotation, part of the resulting flows settle into an inner dense disc\nwhich becomes more susceptible to mass transfer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Dec 2013 21:05:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 22 Dec 2013 14:56:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-24"}
